rep_input: Clinically, what are the on-label points I should know about Trodelvy in HR+/HER2- after prior CDK4/6?
model_output: Trodelvy is indicated for HR+/HER2- metastatic breast cancer after prior endocrine therapy and at least two systemic treatments, including a CDK4/6 inhibitor. It’s important to assess the patient’s overall health, prior lines of therapy, and specific treatment goals. Please email me the SmPC or EPAR for any specific figures or further detailed questions.
